%h1 Campaign collection

%p
  Your campaign for 
  %i
    =@campaign.book.administrative_title
  targeting
  =number_to_currency(@campaign.target_amount, precision: 0)
  by
  =@campaign.target_date.strftime '%-m/%-d/%Y'
  has been closed and we have started the process of collecting the donations.
  You will be notified when the collection process has completed.
